  "remarks": "In detention in Algeria since Oct. 2004. Former member of the GSPC listed as The Organization of Al-Qaida in the Islamic Maghreb (QE.T.14.01).Father’s name: Abdellah. Mother’s name: Draham Belanchi. Photograph and fingerprints available for inclusion in INTERPOL-UNSC Special Notice. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 27 Jul. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by the UN 1267 Committee on 4 December 2003 (amended 7 April 2008, 16 May 2011, 6 Dec 2019)",
